WITH movie_aggregates AS (
    SELECT 
        mt.id AS movie_id,
        mt.title, 
        mt.production_year,
        COUNT(DISTINCT mc.company_id) AS total_companies,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT cn.name, ', ') AS company_names,
        COUNT(DISTINCT mk.keyword_id) AS total_keywords,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT kw.keyword, ', ') AS keywords
    FROM 
        aka_title mt
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_companies mc ON mt.id = mc.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        company_name cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_keyword mk ON mt.id = mk.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        keyword kw ON mk.keyword_id = kw.id
    WHERE 
        mt.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2023
    GROUP BY 
        mt.id, mt.title, mt.production_year
),
actor_aggregates AS (
    SELECT 
        ak.person_id,
        ak.name,
        COUNT(DISTINCT ci.movie_id) AS total_movies,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT mt.title, ', ') AS movies
    FROM 
        aka_name ak
    JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON ak.person_id = ci.person_id
    JOIN 
        aka_title mt ON ci.movie_id = mt.id
    GROUP BY 
        ak.person_id, ak.name
)
SELECT 
    ma.movie_id,
    ma.title,
    ma.production_year,
    ma.total_companies,
    ma.company_names,
    ma.total_keywords,
    ma.keywords,
    aa.person_id,
    aa.name AS actor_name,
    aa.total_movies,
    aa.movies
FROM 
    movie_aggregates ma
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON ma.movie_id = ci.movie_id
JOIN 
    actor_aggregates aa ON ci.person_id = aa.person_id
ORDER BY 
    ma.production_year DESC, ma.title

LEFT JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "aka_title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
WHERE "aka_title"."production_year" >= 2000 AND "aka_title"."production_year" <= 2023
GROUP BY "aka_title"."id", "aka_title"."title", "aka_title"."production_year") AS "t3"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" AS "cast_info0" ON "t3"."MOVIE_ID" = "cast_info0"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "aka_name"."person_id" AS "PERSON_ID", "aka_name"."name" AS "NAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."movie_id") AS "TOTAL_MOVIES", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_title0"."title", ', ') AS "MOVIES"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_title" AS "aka_title0" ON "s1"."movie_id" = "aka_title0"."id"
GROUP BY "aka_name"."person_id", "aka_name"."name") AS "t5" ON "cast_info0"."person_id" = "t5"."PERSON_ID"
ORDER BY "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t3"."TITLE"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "movie_id", "title", "imdb_index", "kind_id", "production_year", "phonetic_code", "episode_of_id", "season_nr", "episode_nr", "note", "md5sum"
FROM "aka_title"

SELECT COALESCE("t3"."MOVIE_ID", "t3"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t3"."TITLE", "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t3"."TOTAL_COMPANIES", "t3"."COMPANY_NAMES", "t3"."TOTAL_KEYWORDS", "t3"."KEYWORDS", "t5"."PERSON_ID", "t5"."NAME" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t5"."TOTAL_MOVIES", "t5"."MOVIES"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_title0"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "aka_title0"."title" AS "TITLE", "aka_title0"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(DISTINCT "movie_companies"."company_id") AS "TOTAL_COMPANIES", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "company_name"."name", ', ') AS "COMPANY_NAMES", COUNT(DISTINCT "movie_keyword"."keyword_id") AS "TOTAL_KEYWORDS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM "aka_title" AS "aka_title0"
LEFT JOIN "movie_companies" ON "aka_title0"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "aka_title0"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
WHERE "aka_title0"."production_year" >= 2000 AND "aka_title0"."production_year" <= 2023
GROUP BY "aka_title0"."id", "aka_title0"."title", "aka_title0"."production_year") AS "t3"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "t3"."MOVIE_ID" = "cast_info"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "aka_name"."person_id" AS "PERSON_ID", "aka_name"."name" AS "NAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info0"."movie_id") AS "TOTAL_MOVIES", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "s1"."title", ', ') AS "MOVIES"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" AS "cast_info0" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info0"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info0"."movie_id" = "s1"."id"
GROUP BY "aka_name"."person_id", "aka_name"."name") AS "t5" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "t5"."PERSON_ID"
ORDER BY "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t3"."TITLE"
